price: 30. Maalinta aan ku odhan  Jahannama: Ma buuxsantay? Oo markaa ay dhihi: Ma jiraan wax dheeraad ah oo la soo wado?
arabic: يَوۡمَ نَقُولُ لِجَهَنَّمَ هَلِ ٱمۡتَلَأۡتِ وَتَقُولُ هَلۡ مِن مَّزِيدٖ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur'an into the Somali language, translated by Abdullah Hasan Jacob.
